Improvement in Dynamic Assessments

Save additional information about dynamic assessments in custom fields on the Assessment object. Previously, you saved information only in the standard fields.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions where Public Sector Solutions is enabled.
